{"tid":697293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特金會】李顯龍：搞特金會開支要1.2億港元 近半係保安使費","createTime":"2018-06-11T01:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T06:32:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7359e621c0adab15a406788ef1ebb3693ca719bd","tid":697293,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180610/large/1528617169_dfa4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180610%2Flarge%2F1528617169_dfa4.jpg&h=cf744721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新加坡總理李顯龍表示，主辦今次美朝歷史性峯會的開支達2,000萬坡元（1.2億港元），近一半費用用於保安支出，他又指今次主辦峯會是顯示了獅城對國際社會的貢獻並「有深遠意義」，新加坡願意花這筆錢 。<br />\n<br />\n李顯龍周日到位於F1維修大樓（F1 Pit Building）的傳媒中心參觀期間指，峯會有助朝鮮半島和平發展新進程，「從我們的角度來看，召開(美朝)峯會非常重要，峯會確定了新軌跡──有利該區安全與穩定發展」。<br />\n<br />\n他指今次峯會花費的2,000萬坡元中，約一半是保安開支。李顯龍今日會與金正恩會面，與特朗普的會面就安排在明天。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180610/58300660\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180610%2F58300660&d=l9VKxDsGp6iGW%2FHX6EPx8Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=19cd9181\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180610%2F58300660&h=dbdb74eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180610/58300660</a>"},{"pid":"16dba67213ba0be3577c5d40b86c834263a34fb9","tid":697293,"uid":35790,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:06:46.000Z","msg":"物超所值"},{"pid":"a979b26586bc13214382451c97a153a87d301c09","tid":697293,"uid":23707,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:07:52.000Z","msg":"抵到爛"},{"pid":"a330021adde1f2f6a61a25b1dc2d9e3d4684ac45","tid":697293,"uid":13534,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"rep